                >2020 [written] Everything but the React</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="./2021">2021 [written] React 18</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdyftlnWm-E&list=PLnc_NxpmOxaP6kHOzL6SVJr58LCTvRwvC">2022 [YouTube] Next 13</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
